title: Blue Ridge Parkway Encourages Visitors to Enjoy the View and Watch the Road (NPS - ...
text: ( Source : NPS - National Park Service ) Date : October 8, 2015 Contact : Leesa Brandon , 828.348.3420 NC/VA -Blue Ridge Parkway rangers and staff plan to welcome approximately two million visitors along the 469-mile scenic route this October.
